text: Sarah Ann Ogilvie (born 10 April 1959) is a Canadian rower. She competed in the women's coxless pair event at the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1959 births Category:Living people Category:Canadian female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Canada Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Seattle
